### النسخة الإنجليزية:

```
🕌 Open Source Project — Salati (Prayer Reminder for Windows)

Hey everyone 👋

I'm Mahmoud, a .NET Developer, and I'm building an open-source desktop app called Salati — a prayer time reminder for Windows users.

📌 What it does:
A lightweight app that runs in the background and reminds you before each prayer time by the exact minutes you choose.

🎯 Key Features:
✅ Auto-fetch prayer times via API or manual input
✅ Custom pre-prayer alerts (per prayer, per minute)
✅ Full control: enable/disable each prayer independently
✅ Adhan sound + Popup notifications
✅ Starts with Windows
✅ Arabic & English support

🛠️ Tech Stack:
C# | .NET 9 | WinForms | 3-Tier Architecture | Aladhan API | JSON | NAudio

👥 Looking for:
- C# developer for Business Logic & Timer scheduling
- C# developer for API integration & local data management
- (Optional) UI/UX enthusiast & tester

📋 Requirements:
- C# & OOP fundamentals
- Git & GitHub basics
- Commitment (~2 hours/day or as agreed)

DM me or comment below if interested! 👇

#CSharp #DotNet #OpenSource #WinForms
```

