## 📁 GitHub README Template

```markdown
# 🕌 Salati — Prayer Time Reminder for Windows

A lightweight, customizable desktop application that reminds you before each prayer time.

## ✨ Features
- 🕐 Auto-fetch prayer times via Aladhan API
- ✏️ Manual prayer time input
- ⏰ Custom pre-prayer alerts (set minutes per prayer)
- 🔊 Adhan sound & popup notifications  
- 🖥️ System tray integration
- 🚀 Starts with Windows
- 🌐 Arabic & English support

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- C# (.NET 9)
- WinForms
- 3-Tier Architecture
- Aladhan API
- NAudio (Sound)
- System.Text.Json

## 📁 Project Structure
[See Architecture Docs]

## 🤝 Contributing
We welcome contributions! Please read our [CONTRIBUTING.md](CONTRIBUTING.md) for guidelines.

